02:38.285 --> 02:40.189
Did you find it?

02:42.045 --> 02:43.746
You scared the crap out of me.

02:44.073 --> 02:45.599
Look at this.

02:46.600 --> 02:47.680
Is that it?

02:50.520 --> 02:53.886
In nomine Patris, et
Filii, et Spiritus Sancti.

03:46.972 --> 03:52.170
